**Benign duplicate** (2 phones sync simultaneously):
→ First succeeds, second reverts harmlessly
→ SQLite updates from blockchain event
→ Zero data loss/duplication

**Malicious replay** (attacker sniffs cellular burst):
→ bundleId already marked → 25k gas revert
→ No state change, no data exposure
→ Attacker burns $0.0004 trying

**Network partition** (half nodes offline):
→ Wait for 3-of-5 quorum → bundle held locally
→ Reconnect → normal reconciliation